<div class='tutorial_header'>
  <div class="modal_claim_wrap">
    <div id="scroll_pane">
      <div id="scrolling_segment">
        <div id="scroll_wrap">
          <div id="panel1" class="scroll_panel" >
            <div class="tutorial_column_left">
              <%= image_tag('/images/tutorials/provider_profile/pp-tutorial-1.png') %>
            </div>
            <div class="tutorial_column_right">
              <h2>Provider Profile Overview</h2>
              <h3>Provider Profile Tutorial</h3>
              <p>
                A comprehensive list of a provider’s overall statistics, license and sanction information, address, scoring rank and so much more. Provider Profile packs the perfect information punch.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="panel2" class="scroll_panel" >
            <div class="tutorial_column_left">
              <%= image_tag('/images/tutorials/provider_profile/pp-tutorial-2.png') %>
            </div>
            <div class="tutorial_column_right">
              <h2>Intelligent Scoring &amp; Risk Levels</h2>
              <h3>Provider Profile Tutorial</h3>
              <p>
                The Nucleus Provider Profile scores each provider on two criteria: the individual provider score and the condition score. Within those two scores are numerous variables, vital statistics, suspect billing patterns and various other data that are all combined to give you the most intelligent scoring and the most accurate risk level available for each provider.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="panel3" class="scroll_panel" >
            <div class="tutorial_column_left">
              <%= image_tag('/images/tutorials/provider_profile/pp-tutorial-3.png') %>
            </div>
            <div class="tutorial_column_right">
              <h2>Billing Stats &amp; Sanction Visualizations</h2>
              <h3>Provider Profile Tutorial</h3>
              <p>
                Get vital billing statistics and easily view existing sanctions against providers. Nucleus looks for billing abnormalities and processes findings in visually rich data fields and widgets to better paint you a picture of the average billing trends, so when those abnormalities are found, they’re dealt with.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="panel4" class="scroll_panel" >
            <div class="tutorial_column_left">
              <%= image_tag('/images/tutorials/provider_profile/pp-tutorial-4.png') %>
            </div>
            <div class="tutorial_column_right">
              <h2>Demographic &amp; Sanction Info</h2>
              <h3>Provider Profile Tutorial</h3>
              <p>
                More than just a snapshot, Nucleus digs deep into the background of each of your providers. Taking into consideration both geographic and demographic information it's able to raise red flags with greater accuracy. And crosschecking databases of federal and state sanctions, you'll know before you pay an existing sanctioned provider.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="panel5" class="scroll_panel" >
            <div class="tutorial_column_left">
              <%= image_tag('/images/tutorials/provider_profile/pp-tutorial-5.png') %>
            </div>
            <div class="tutorial_column_right">
              <h2>Google Maps &amp; Web Searches</h2>
              <h3>Provider Profile Tutorial</h3>
              <p>
                Atop the Profile Page is a Google search tool. Type your request, hit enter and instantly get results. Nucleus also includes Google Maps and a Street View for complete address information of each provider, located under the "Address" tab.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

